FBIS3-27009 "drchi033_k_94007" FBIS-CHI-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Former NPC Vice Chairman Liu Ningyi Dies OW1702133494 Beijing XINHUA in English 1313 GMT 17 Feb 94 OW1702133494 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, February 17 (XINHUA) -- Liu Ningyi, former vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of the Third National People's Congress, died of illness here on February 15 at the age of 87. Liu Ningyi was an outstanding member of the Communist Party of China, a proletarian revolutionary and an outstanding leader of the workers' movement.
